headline: T. ROWE PRICE GROUP REPORTS PRELIMINARY MONTH-END ASSETS UNDER MANAGEMENT FOR SEPTEMBER 2025
summary: T. Rowe Price Group, Inc. (NASDAQ-GS: TROW) announced preliminary September month-end assets under management of $1.77 trillion. Preliminary net outflows for September 2025 were $2.0 billion. For the quarter-ended September 2025, net outflows were $7.9 billion, including $0.8 billion of manager-driven distributions.
